##Capstone Project 1: Financial Ledger
The Accounting application is a Java based tool aimed to use by people to efficiently track amd manage their finances.
This application allow users to create reports of their expenses and earnings and add new deposits or payments.
Using transactions.csv users can retrieve and update transactions across different sessions.

###Features
- Transaction Update: straightforward and user friendly process of adding new deposits and payments to transaction file
- Ledger View: categorized preview of all transactions entries and separate review of deposits or payments separatly.
- Custom Reports: option to create reports to specific time frame or vendor name;
- Search Engine: a flexible search tools allow to filter reports on a multiple criteria such as: vendor, strat and end day,
amount, description;

**Code examples if filtering report by Vendor name:**
```private static void displayByVendorName() {
           System.out.println("Enter the name of the vendor you would like to search for:");
